d: 2019-03-14T12:45:22+00:00
ID: 1903.06012v1
Title: Deep Learning Methods for Science Education Assessment
Authors: Maria Rodriguez, James Liu, Anna Kowalski
Categories: cs.CY, physics.ed-ph
Abstract: We present a novel framework for automated assessment in science education using deep learning techniques. Our system analyzes student responses to open-ended physics questions and provides formative feedback. Evaluated on a dataset of 15,000 student responses from introductory physics courses, our model achieves 87% agreement with expert human graders.
PDF: https://arxiv.org/pdf/1903.06012v1

