Title: Gamification in Physics Education: A Systematic Review
Authors: Thomas Brown, Wei Chen, Fatima Al-Hassan
Categories: physics.ed-ph
Abstract: This systematic review examines the effectiveness of gamification strategies in physics education at the undergraduate level. We analyzed 47 peer-reviewed studies published between 2015 and 2022, finding moderate positive effects on student engagement and learning outcomes.
PDF: https://arxiv.org/pdf/2211.04283v1

